{
  "chapter": 33,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十三回　蛇蝎美人。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨镖",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨神",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨神",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹！饶了他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放火焰",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大头鬼",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨镖",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秦淮门",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这是在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南第一美人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你找什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才我好像看到一个红发青脸之人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜我叫什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘是跟在下说笑话了，人的名字怎可乱猜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下从未与姑娘会过面，而且也没听说……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没听说过江湖上有你这么一号。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你看到这面具，还不知道我是谁吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨神",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨镖",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨镖",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么，我来此已经两天了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十五夜到今天十七夜，刚好整整两天，其实我也是太紧张了，这制钱上的毒虽然厉害，但不见血是没有关系的，我不过怕你不知道，拿在手中把手指割破，增添麻烦就是了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南京板鸭",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的小爷！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "的一声，把一大口的食物咽下肚去了，好像是答应了小女的叫爷声，那小女刚一瞪眼，展白却嘘了一口气道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "巧不巧地，展白一声",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那布衣少女见自己无意中叫出一声",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "地一声竟似答应，无形中占了自己的便宜，忙道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呃！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘，你发现了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三花聚顶",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下何出此言？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下说这话是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "轰！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "竟是她！竟是她……真令人不敢相信……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "红粉骷髅，鬼面娇娃",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "红粉骷髅，鬼面娇娃",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魔鬼岛",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "红粉骷髅，鬼面魔女",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你不会相信，可是等到你相信的时候，后悔就已经晚了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你又想跑吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少陪了！但你别得意，'海外三煞'一到，便是你丧命之时……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无情碧剑",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无情碧剑",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孟少爷为什么不听主人的命令行事，难道他疯了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他可不是真的疯了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想他若不疯，怎么会连公子小姐陷入阵中呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他这又是为什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨神",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨神",
      "tone": "陈述",
